origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "TechInnovation.evaluate_capability",
        "description": "评估公司的技术创新能力，基于创新能力和技术转化率进行综合评价。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "innovation_capability",
                "type": "FLOAT",
                "description": "公司的创新能力评分。"
            },
            {
                "name": "conversion_rate",
                "type": "FLOAT",
                "description": "技术转化率，表示研发成果转化为实际产品的效率。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "final_evaluation",
                "description": "最终的技术创新能力评估结果。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "TechInnovation.get_tech_conversion_rate",
        "description": "获取指定公司的技术转化率，即研发成果转化为实际产品的效率。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "company_name",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "公司名称。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "conversion_rate",
                "description": "技术转化率。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "TechInnovation.analyze_RnD_and_patents",
        "description": "分析公司的研发投资和专利数量，评估其创新能力。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "RnD_investment",
                "type": "FLOAT",
                "description": "公司的研发投资金额。"
            },
            {
                "name": "patents",
                "type": "INTEGER",
                "description": "公司拥有的专利数量。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "innovation_capability",
                "description": "评估得出的创新能力评分。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "TechInnovation.get_RnD_and_patents",
        "description": "获取指定公司的研发投资和专利数量。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "company_name",
                "description": "公司名称。",
                "type": "STRING"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "RnD_investment",
                "description": "公司的研发投资金额。"
            },
            {
                "name": "patents",
                "description": "公司拥有的专利数量。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "TechInnovation.predict_future_innovation",
        "description": "基于历史数据预测公司未来的创新能力。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "historical_data",
                "type": "ARRAY",
                "description": "公司过去几年的创新能力数据。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "future_innovation_prediction",
                "description": "预测的未来创新能力评分。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "TechInnovation.compare_competitors",
        "description": "比较指定公司与竞争对手的技术创新能力。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "company_name",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "公司名称。"
            },
            {
                "name": "competitor_names",
                "type": "ARRAY",
                "description": "竞争对手的公司名称列表。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "comparison_result",
                "description": "公司与竞争对手的技术创新能力比较结果。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "TechInnovation.get_industry_average",
        "description": "获取指定行业内公司的平均技术创新能力。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "industry_name",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "行业名称。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "industry_average_innovation",
                "description": "行业内公司的平均技术创新能力评分。"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
